---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="User Guide — xCrypto24" description="Learn how to use xCrypto24 to track memecoins, scan new tokens, check safety scores, and monitor your portfolio." keywords="xcrypto24 guide, how to use crypto tracker, memecoin scanner guide, token safety check">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"WebPage","name":"User Guide — xCrypto24","url":"https://xcrypto24.com/guide","description":"Learn how to use xCrypto24 to track memecoins, scan new tokens, check safety scores, and monitor your portfolio."})} />
  <div style="max-width:800px;margin:2rem auto;padding:2rem;">
    <h1 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">📖 xCrypto24 User Guide</h1>
    <p style="color:#94a3b8;margin-bottom:2rem;">Everything you need to know about tracking memecoins with xCrypto24.</p>

    <h2 style="color:#f59e0b;font-size:1.2rem;margin:2rem 0 0.8rem;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b;padding-left:0.8rem;">Getting Started</h2>
    <p style="color:#cbd5e1;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">xCrypto24 is a free memecoin tracker focused on Solana tokens. No signup, no API keys, no cost. Just add a coin and start tracking.</p>
    <ul style="color:#94a3b8;line-height:2.2;padding-left:1.5rem;">
      <li>Go to the <a href="/coins" style="color:#f59e0b;">Coins Dashboard</a></li>
      <li>Click <strong style="color:#10b981;">+ Add Coin</strong></li>
      <li>Type the coin name and hit <strong style="color:#8b5cf6;">🔍 Auto-fill</strong> to pull data from DexScreener</li>
      <li>Save — your coin is now tracked</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="color:#f59e0b;font-size:1.2rem;margin:2rem 0 0.8rem;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b;padding-left:0.8rem;">Fetching Live Data</h2>
    <p style="color:#cbd5e1;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">Once you have coins added, use the action buttons to pull real-time data:</p>
    <ul style="color:#94a3b8;line-height:2.2;padding-left:1.5rem;">
      <li><strong style="color:#8b5cf6;">⚡ Fetch All Coins Data</strong> — pulls price, volume, liquidity, buys/sells, holders from DexScreener + RugCheck for all enabled coins</li>
      <li><strong style="color:#06b6d4;">📜 Fetch History</strong> — downloads hourly and daily OHLCV candle data from GeckoTerminal for charts</li>
      <li><strong style="color:#10b981;">🛡️ RugCheck All</strong> — runs safety analysis on all coins (score, holders, bundles, rug status)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="color:#f59e0b;font-size:1.2rem;margin:2rem 0 0.8rem;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b;padding-left:0.8rem;">Understanding Status & Trend</h2>
    <p style="color:#cbd5e1;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;"><strong>Status</strong> reflects short-term movement (1-5 hours). <strong>Trend</strong> reflects longer-term direction (1 week to 1 month).</p>

    <div style="overflow-x:auto;margin:1rem 0;">
      <table style="width:100%;font-size:0.85rem;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #334155;">
            <th style="text-align:left;padding:0.5rem;color:#94a3b8;">Label</th>
            <th style="text-align:left;padding:0.5rem;color:#94a3b8;">Meaning</th>
            <th style="text-align:left;padding:0.5rem;color:#94a3b8;">Change</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody style="color:#cbd5e1;">
          <tr><td style="padding:0.4rem;color:#10b981;">Mooning</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">Extreme upward movement</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">≥ +20%</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:0.4rem;color:#4ade80;">Breaking Out</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">Strong breakout confirmed</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">≥ +15%</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:0.4rem;color:#4ade80;">Pumping Hard</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">Significant upward pressure</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">≥ +10%</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:0.4rem;color:#4ade80;">Pumping</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">Healthy upward movement</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">≥ +5%</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:0.4rem;color:#4ade80;">Creeping Up</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">Slight positive momentum</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">+2% to +5%</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:0.4rem;color:#f59e0b;">Consolidating</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">Sideways / stable</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">-2% to +2%</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:0.4rem;color:#f97316;">Bleeding</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">Slow decline</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">-2% to -5%</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:0.4rem;color:#ef4444;">Dumping</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">Selling pressure</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">≤ -5%</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:0.4rem;color:#dc2626;">Dumping Hard</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">Heavy selling</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">≤ -10%</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:0.4rem;color:#dc2626;">Crashing</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">Severe drop</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">≤ -20%</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:0.4rem;color:#7f1d1d;">Almost Nuked</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">Near-total collapse</td><td style="padding:0.4rem;">≤ -30%</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p style="color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.8;margin:1rem 0;">Special overrides: <strong style="color:#a855f7;">Profit Taking</strong> (up 30% in 24h but dropping in the last hour) and <strong style="color:#a855f7;">Dead Cat Bounce</strong> (down 30% in 24h but bouncing in the last hour).</p>

    <h2 style="color:#f59e0b;font-size:1.2rem;margin:2rem 0 0.8rem;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b;padding-left:0.8rem;">Tech Analysis Charts</h2>
    <p style="color:#cbd5e1;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">The <a href="/admin/analysis" style="color:#f59e0b;">Analysis page</a> shows candlestick charts for each coin. Use the <strong>Duration dropdown</strong> to zoom in or out:</p>
    <ul style="color:#94a3b8;line-height:2.2;padding-left:1.5rem;">
      <li><strong>10m–1h:</strong> Very short-term view (last few candles)</li>
      <li><strong>2h–12h:</strong> Intraday view</li>
      <li><strong>1d–3d:</strong> Multi-day view</li>
      <li><strong>1w–1M:</strong> Long-term trend view (uses daily candles)</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.8;margin-top:1rem;">Mini charts on the right show Market Cap, Liquidity, and Holder count over time. These populate after 2+ "Fetch All" runs.</p>

    <h2 style="color:#f59e0b;font-size:1.2rem;margin:2rem 0 0.8rem;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b;padding-left:0.8rem;">Safety Scores (RugCheck)</h2>
    <p style="color:#cbd5e1;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">Each coin gets a safety rating from RugCheck.xyz:</p>
    <ul style="color:#94a3b8;line-height:2.2;padding-left:1.5rem;">
      <li><span style="color:#10b981;">🟢 Safe (0-100)</span> — low risk indicators</li>
      <li><span style="color:#f59e0b;">🟡 Caution (101-500)</span> — some risk factors present</li>
      <li><span style="color:#ef4444;">🔴 Risky (500+)</span> — high risk, proceed with caution</li>
      <li><span style="color:#dc2626;">🚨 RUGGED</span> — confirmed rug pull</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="color:#f59e0b;font-size:1.2rem;margin:2rem 0 0.8rem;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b;padding-left:0.8rem;">Data Sources</h2>
    <ul style="color:#94a3b8;line-height:2.2;padding-left:1.5rem;">
      <li><strong>DexScreener</strong> — real-time price, volume, liquidity, buys/sells, pair data</li>
      <li><strong>GeckoTerminal</strong> — OHLCV candlestick history (hourly + daily)</li>
      <li><strong>RugCheck.xyz</strong> — safety scores, holder analysis, bundle detection</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="color:#f59e0b;font-size:1.2rem;margin:2rem 0 0.8rem;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b;padding-left:0.8rem;">Tips</h2>
    <ul style="color:#94a3b8;line-height:2.2;padding-left:1.5rem;">
      <li>Run <strong>Fetch All</strong> regularly to build up tracker history for better trend analysis</li>
      <li>Use <strong>Update Trends</strong> (1-5hr) for short-term status, <strong>Set Trend</strong> (1w-1m) for long-term direction</li>
      <li>Check the <strong>Top Holder %</strong> — if one wallet holds 20%+, that's a rug risk</li>
      <li>Watch <strong>Buys vs Sells ratio</strong> — healthy coins have balanced or buy-heavy ratios</li>
      <li>If a coin shows "No bundles" in traders, that's a positive sign (no insider networks detected)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="color:#f59e0b;font-size:1.2rem;margin:2rem 0 0.8rem;border-left:3px solid #f59e0b;padding-left:0.8rem;">Your Data</h2>
    <p style="color:#cbd5e1;line-height:1.8;">All data is stored locally in your browser session and our database. No account needed, no personal information collected. You can add, edit, or delete coins at any time. See our <a href="/privacy" style="color:#f59e0b;">Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>

    <div style="margin-top:2rem;padding:1.2rem;background:#1e293b;border:1px solid #334155;border-radius:8px;text-align:center;">
      <p style="color:#94a3b8;margin-bottom:0.8rem;">Ready to start tracking?</p>
      <a href="/coins" style="display:inline-block;padding:0.7rem 1.5rem;background:#f59e0b;color:#000;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">Go to Coins Dashboard →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
